Single Homepage Traffic From Organic Search

This metric is an indicator of our homepage’s effectiveness over time.

The median daily percentage of homepage entries from organic search that bounced on desktop devices was 34% during the past 180 days.
The median daily percentage of homepage entries from organic search that bounced on mobile devices was 45% during the past 180 days.
